
- General:
	All data access is done before any displaying.

- Groups:
	A user is a member of the grade_[grade] group automatically.  If a user is a member of admin_all, they have all administration rights.

- Display:
	One display instance is created per intrabox, and one for the pane.

- Data:
	A Result is an abstract object which may represent MySQL or LDAP results, or something else.

